位若再度入市買入澳元，提供他們所需的對口單子，形成了Liquidity Zone。<br />\n<br />\n因此我們的trade plan是，若果稍後或明天價格重回0.6713之下的話，我們便買入澳元兌美元，若價位跌穿Liquidity Zone的話便止蝕平倉。"},{"pid":"4910daceb2eaae9aebf83df6a8732d421748abb5","tid":2046884,"uid":11944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f564eca5d0ce1d9b36d3e3a6edf044137a7005b","tid":2046884,"uid":43407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T16:58:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/notes/%E5%A1%B5%E7%BF%BC%E7%9E%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AFk%E6%88%BF/%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%B6%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E9%99%B7%E9%98%B1%E6%BE%B3%E5%85%83%E5%85%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83/2659902197625041/?av=1858365591112043&amp;eav=Afbwdk-4xCHtdO6CLCQS2EcIyQBGEx7wYHh3JI96OJpxTnvg3JlA51vqCLG2eIC_N9sGcDBwz6XWjG_Fp1ydM78n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnotes%2F%25E5%25A1%25B5%25E7%25BF%25BC%25E7%259E%25AC%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%258C%25AFk%25E6%2588%25BF%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2588%25B6%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E9%2599%25B7%25E9%2598%25B1%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%2585%258C%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%2583%2F2659902197625041%2F%3Fav%3D1858365591112043%26eav%3DAfbwdk-4xCHtdO6CLCQS2EcIyQBGEx7wYHh3JI96OJpxTnvg3JlA51vqCLG2eIC_N9sGcDBwz6XWjG_Fp1ydM78n&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns80uhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=344f62d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/notes/%E5%A1%B5%E7%BF%BC%E7%9E%AC%E7%9A%84%E5%A4%96%E5%8C%AFk%E6%88%BF/%E5%A4%A7%E6%88%B6%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E9%99%B7%E9%98%B1%E6%BE%B3%E5%85%83%E5%85%8C%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83/2659902197625041/?av=1858365591112043&amp;eav=Afbwdk-4xCHtdO6CLCQS2EcIyQBGEx7wYHh3JI96OJpxTnvg3JlA51vqCLG2eIC_N9sGcDBwz6XWjG_Fp1ydM78n</a><br />\n<br />\n今日要介紹的是一個直盤澳元兌美元的大戶價格陷阱。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/okodtnc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fokodtnc.png&h=94fc2cab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實澳元兌美元長線自從三月的重挫後，兩個月內已經完全收復失地。小時圖上可見，今早周一開市澳元急速上升超過一百點，剛剛更突破了今天較早時創下的短線阻力0.6772。<br />\n<br />\n相信很多